    <body>
      <section eId="sec_884">
        <num>884</num>
        <heading>Permit coordination and assistance to applicants</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_884__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>facilitating contacts for the applicant with state agencies\nresponsible for processing and reviewing permit applications;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_884__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>arranging conferences to clarify the interest and requirements of\nany such state agency with respect to permit applications;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_884__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>considering with state agencies the feasibility of consolidating\nhearings and data required of the applicant;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_884__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>assisting the applicant in the resolution of outstanding issues\nidentified by state agencies, including delays experienced in permit\nreview; and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_884__subsec_e">
          <num>(e)</num>
          <content>
            <p>coordinating federal, state, and local permit review actions to\nthe extent practicable.\n  * NB Authority of office terminated per ยง 893 December 31, 1995\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
